[SIZE=5]PaydayLib[/SIZE]

[SIZE=5][COLOR="#FF0000"]**DEDICATED SERVER ONLY**[/COLOR][/SIZE]

Server Economy mod for 7 days to die dedicated servers.  This mod allows your players to earn points for their time spent on your server.  These points can then be used to purchase "products" that have been added by other mods. (please see the "Addons" Section below.)

