[SIZE=4]Console Commands[/SIZE]

[INDENT]
[B]paydaylib info[/B] Displays the current configuration settings for PaydayLib

[B]paydaylib reload[/B] Reloads the PaydayLib Config and Player Data

[B]paydaylib enabletimer[/B] Enables the PaydayLib User Pay Timer

[B]paydaylib disabletimer[/B] Disables the PaydayLib User Pay Timer

[B]paydaylib currency <currency_name>[/B] Changes the name of the in game Currency (The Currency name defaults to "Coins")

[B]paydaylib rate <amount>[/B] Sets the amount of points a player receives each real-world Minute.

[B]paydaylib startrate <starting_balance>[/B] Sets the amount of points a player receives the first time they join the server.

[B]pdlsetprice <ProductName> <amount>[/B] Sets the price for a product
[/INDENT]

[SIZE=4]Chat Commands[/SIZE]

[INDENT]
[B]!balance[/B] Show your current balance

[B]!listproducts[/B] Shows you a list of purchasble products

[B]!buy <ProductMame>[/B] Buy the product <ProductName>

[B]!pay <PlayerName> <amount>[/B] Transfer <amount> coins from your balance to <PlayerName>

[/INDENT]

[SIZE=4]Quick Setup Guide[/SIZE]

[INDENT]
Ensure you have admin rights and run the following commands

This will set up Paydaylib with a currency called "MyCoolNameForCoins".  Each player will receive 50 MyCoolNameForCoins when they first join, and an additional 1 MyCoolNameForCoins per minute they are on the server.

[/INDENT]

[CODE]
paydaylib currency MyCoolNameForCoins

paydaylib rate 1

paydaylib startrate 50

paydaylib enabletimer

[/CODE]

